sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client<br/>(In-Cluster Service)
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Upstream as Upstream Application<br/>(localhost) HTTP

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 1: Authenticated Request Proxying
        Client->>Proxy: HTTPS Request (8443/TCP)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / Client Cert / OIDC JWT
        Note over Proxy: Path Filter: check --ignore-paths
        Note over Proxy: AuthN: TokenReview / x509 / OIDC
        Proxy->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/authentication.k8s.io/v1/tokenreviews<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>Proxy: TokenReview Response<br/>(user info, groups)
        Note over Proxy: AuthZ: SubjectAccessReview
        Proxy->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/authorization.k8s.io/v1/subjectaccessreviews<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>Proxy: SubjectAccessReview Response<br/>(allowed: true/false)
        Note over Proxy: Inject auth headers<br/>(X-Remote-User, X-Remote-Group)
        Proxy->>Upstream: Forward Request (localhost)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS/h2c
        Upstream-->>Proxy: Response
        Proxy-->>Client: HTTPS Response (8443/TCP)
    end

    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>(openshift-monitoring)<br/>prometheus-k8s SA

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Prom,Upstream: Flow 2: Prometheus Metrics Scraping
        Prom->>Proxy: GET /metrics (8443/TCP HTTPS)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (prometheus-k8s SA)
        Note over Proxy: AuthN: TokenReview
        Proxy->>K8sAPI: POST tokenreviews<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>Proxy: TokenReview Response<br/>(system:serviceaccount:openshift-monitoring:prometheus-k8s)
        Note over Proxy: Hardcoded Authorizer:<br/>ALLOW prometheus-k8s SA<br/>on GET /metrics
        Proxy->>Upstream: GET /metrics (localhost)<br/>HTTP (no auth)
        Upstream-->>Proxy: Metrics Response<br/>(Prometheus format)
        Proxy-->>Prom: HTTPS Response (8443/TCP)
    end
